[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Toolbar position]]
A [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Advanced Settings|setting]] that allows you to set position of the main [[en/Manual/Game interface#the-menu-bar|toolbar]].

== Description ==
Align position of the main toolbar to the left side, center or right side of the screen.
This patch changes only user interface and does not affect the gameplay. If selected on multiplayer, it will not affect any other players.

== Use ==
This feature is set to 0 by default. It can be set to 0, 1 or 2, which means left side, center or right side of the screen respectively. You can change it through either the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Configuring patches/Interface|configure patches -> Interface]] window or use the following syntax in [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Openttd.cfg]]:
<pre>[patches]
toolbar_pos = 0</pre>


